Management to prepare and submit semestral inventory reports;


Utilized the RIS in the issuance of materials and prepare the SSMI as a basis of the Municipal Accountant to draw a JEV;

Municipal Accountant and General Services Officer – Designate to maintain SLC and Stock Cards, respectively, and reconcile the same monthly; and

