It is recommended that the Municipality considers the following:

Review personnel requirement of Treasurer’s Office to implement the code including the provision on License Inspector;

Device the sworn statement form to facilitate compliance of the taxpayer on the declaration of revenue in obtaining business permit and residence certificate;

Review certain provisions especially on Cart or Sledge Registration Fee; Dog License Fee; Permit Fee on Agricultural Machinery and Other Heavy Equipment;  Permit fee for the Conduct of Group Activities; Fighting Cock License Fee;  Permit fee on Profession not requiring Government Examination; and Mayor’s Clearance to transport and ship various animals and goods;

Adopt proper and clear procedure on how to implement certain provision of the code; and


Review the policy on slaughter fee in the absence of a Municipal Slaughterhouse.

In consideration of the foregoing observations, we recommended the following:
